window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Now, the quest is on. Objective: Find the dragon before time runs out.</b></p> <p>With sparse details, he’ll depend on the help of an old friend to complete this hunt. It’s going to feel like a bunch of grinding, but victory is imminent. At least, it has to be...or the last dragon in the land will be gone - forever.</p> <p>Each level gets him closer to a cure, because time is running out for everyone, including our cursed hero. What Illume discovers will shock even the most skilled player.</p> <p><i>Warning: This book contains unapologetic humor, dragons, and GameLit elements to thrill seekers of a good time who don’t take themselves or life too seriously.</i></p>"; 
